titleInfo.title: Harold E. Nutter, Inc. v. Korte Construction Company et. al.
titleInfo.subTitle: STIPULATION and ORDER signed by Judge John A. Mendez on 5/10/2013 ORDERING 20 All proceedings in this case, including Korte Construction Company Motion to Dismiss and related deadlines, are STAYED pending completion of the mediation currently scheduled for 6/12/2013 before Donald L. Sullivan. Within 14 days after the completion of mediation, the parties will update the Court, in writing, on the outcome of mediation. If the parties have not reached a settlement at that time, the stay will no longer be in effect and the Court shall reschedule the hearing on Korte's Motion to Dismiss, and all related deadlines. (Reader, L)
